name: Boston |  1 Bedroom  | Patio | Full-Kitchen (III)
neighborhood_overview:
The South End is a historical neighborhood with excellent restaurants. The Spanish Tapas Toro is right on our block (great tapas). We also have Mike's in our block which is an excellent breakfast dinner (recommended). Across the street there is Equator (really good Thai Food) and Seyo (Sushi).

In the next block there is a Seven Eleven, a convenience store, a Walgreens Pharmacy, Flour Bakery & Cafe (recommended) and many other wonderful restaurants at a walking distance.
description:
Condominium with Patio, walking distance to Copley, Back Bay Station, Whole Foods and access to Mass Pike. Close to restaurants, shopping and arts.

The space
This bedroom is one of three bedrooms being rented in my 1600 square feet (145 square meters). Let me know if you need additional space.

The unit is a ground level unit. Easy access from the front and from the patio on the back.

All the bathrooms are shared. There is no private bathroom in this condominium.
